Name: hscrollbar

Details:

Syntax:

Types:

Function:
`Figure hscrollbar(Figure f, FProperty props ...)`

Synopsis:

Description:

Embed figure `f` in a horizontal scrollbar.

Also see [scrollbar] and [vscrollbar].

Examples:

<figure s1.png>
box1 = box(size(200,100), fillColor("Blue"), resizable(false));
render(hscrollbar(box1));
</figure>
![s1](s1.png)

<warning> 2 scrollbars? </warning>

